title: New Edition - "Home Again"
description:
Home Again is the sixth studio album by American R&B/Pop group New Edition, released by MCA Records in 1996.

Group members are:
Ronnie DeVoe
Bobby Brown
Ricky Bell
Michael Bivins
Johnny Gill
Ralph Tresvant
